channel.description: Thank you for subscribing and stopping by to view my channel. I'm just a average Joe just giving my personal thoughts on a wide range of topics. On my channel if you show respect then you shall receive respect. I don't like or tolerate racism of any sort on my channel so if that is your goal to spread hate please go elsewhere with it. I try to reach a crowd with a open mind that are willing to speak on issues with a logical set of mind and use common sense when approaching topics. If you like my channel then subscribe and spread it to your friends on Youtube, Facebook, & Twitter. Thank you for your time.
